"Mrs Claudia Neubauer, Fondation Sciences Citoyennes, speaks at the EISRI Summit on the Role of the Media in Responsible Research and Innovation. Trinity College Dublin - 25-26 February 2013.

The European Intersectoral Summit on Research and Innovation is a European meeting organised by the Atomium Culture every eighteen months dedicated to research and innovation. It brings together over 200 delegates from across Europe and is designed to create a unique opportunity for intersectoral and interdisciplinary discussions between leading stakeholders."


